title: Dishonored 2 RePack by BlackBox
description:
RELEASE NOTES

STEAMPUNKS are proud to bring you the first release including
a real Denuvo license generator with untouched game executable.
Your license will be regenerated if needed (hw change, os updates)
Enjoy The Power We just gave you.

Reprise your role as a supernatural assassin in Dishonored 2.
Declared a "masterpiece" by Eurogamer and hailed
"a must-play revenge tale" by Game Informer, Dishonored 2 is the
follow up to Arkane's 1st-person action blockbuster & winner
of 100+ 'Game of the Year' awards, Dishonored.

Winner, Best Action Adventure Game, The Game Awards 2016

System Requirements:

OS: Windows 7/8/10 (64-bit versions)
Processor: Intel Core i5-2400/AMD FX-8320 or better
Memory: 8 GB RAM
Graphics: NVIDIA GTX 660 2GB/AMD Radeon HD 7970 3GB or better
Storage: 60 GB available space

Features

     Do not cut / no recoded;
     Game archives are not opened;
     Game version: 1.77.5.0;
     Additions: Bonus for Pre-Order;
     In the directory with the game installed, the "Original" folder is created. It contains the medicine and original files (to install another tablet);
     Installation time ~ 20 minutes on HDD (depends on PC);
     The game requires Steam installed!
